{"tid":2352098,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟應唔應該逼另一半做野？","createTime":"2021-01-03T18:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T06:41:31.000Z","uid":140688,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7bedd24810d5bc47fec4860fdbb722d2e08638f7","tid":2352098,"uid":140688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"好多野都會想另一半主動做，覺得講左出口就好似逼人做野咁，搞到成日自己收收埋埋d失落情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如最近男友同我講佢倒數想同大學frd過，問我俾唔俾佢去。我內心想佢同我倒數嘅，但係我口頭上就俾佢去，因為我個諗法係：佢問得我即係想同大學frd過多於同我過，咁既然佢自己心入面都有優先次序，逼佢同我過到時佢睇到d frd post曬story玩得好開心又可能會覺得好可惜無參與到，跟住我就會收埋左件事但事實上係唔開心的。 <br />\n<br />\n究竟我咁樣相處係咪好有問題？係唔係應該向佢坦白講下我睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bdeae82ca9083b1d20b1c236603386c8702166","tid":2352098,"uid":33874,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"想點咪講囉屌<br />\n一係就分手啦"},{"pid":"d99bbc44ce41de502cddb9ea3963db4aa894bbbf","tid":2352098,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"有問題"},{"pid":"73bd439be5d911937e9a0f6edb047daebfc1c453","tid":2352098,"uid":140688,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"82bdeae82ca9083b1d20b1c236603386c8702166","tid":2352098,"uid":33874,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"想點咪講囉屌<br />\n一係就分手啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"但咁樣唔似焗人陪我咩 佢問得即係心中已經覺得想同frd過大於同我過。我就係成日有呢種諗法所以無坦白講想佢陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe5ae74fad9a226f65d183518390f1bfd7da71e","tid":2352098,"uid":140688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d99bbc44ce41de502cddb9ea3963db4aa894bbbf","tid":2352098,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"有問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:25:46.000Z","ms